    <section class="demos-intro" data-section-key="intro">
      <h1>Software when no off-the-shelf product fits</h1>
      <p class="lead">Some workflows can't be forced into standard software: the form that mirrors your approvals, the internal tool that knows exactly your process. I build that software to measure, modern, fast, and in a way you understand and own afterwards. And because I run the servers underneath myself, I don't develop past your infrastructure.</p>
    </section>

